content.html: Just landed at MSY from JFK. Walking to our car, I overheard a couple bickering. Man: ‘Stop telling people you’re positive. You’re not contagious.’ Woman: ‘But I feel guilty and I think I should.’ Man: ‘Don’t tell anyone or we won’t be able to do anything.’ 1/2
content.value:
Just landed at MSY from JFK. Walking to our car, I overheard a couple bickering.

Man: ‘Stop telling people you’re positive. You’re not contagious.’

Woman: ‘But I feel guilty and I think I should.’

Man: ‘Don’t tell anyone or we won’t be able to do anything.’

1/2
